@NODE Preface "1.1  Preface"
@{u}@{b}1.1  Preface@{uu}@{ub}

IntuiCookie is a program that will display fortune cookies.

Some people might say that a MUI fortune cookie program is overkill.  I don't think so.

Just @{"install" LINK Installation} IntuiCookie and draw your own conclusions.

If you don't like MUI, there is also a Reqtools version available.  I am also prepared to give the sourcecode to anybody who is interested in writing and supporting a version for other GUI libraries.

__________
@{i}Pohls' Law:
Nothing is so good that somebody, somewhere, will not hate it.@{ui}

@ENDNODE





@NODE Features "1.2  Why should I use IntuiCookie?"
@{u}@{b}1.2  Why should I use IntuiCookie?@{uu}@{ub}

· IntuiCookie uses a (highly-configurable) MUI window to display the cookie.
· IntuiCookie can be configured via tooltypes and menus.
· There are over numerous different tooltypes to configure the look and behaviour of IntuiCookie even further than the MUI Prefs allow.
· It comes with CookHash, a MUI hash file program.
· IntuiCookie and CookHash are localized.
· Formatting characters are supported.

@ENDNODE





